Data Distributions

Data Distributions

Known probability distributions

set.seed(12345)
norm <- rnorm(n = 200, mean = 10, sd = 1)
binom <- rbinom(n = 200, size = 20, prob = 0.5)
pois <- rpois(n = 200, lambda = 3)
exp <- rexp(n = 200, rate = 100)

par(mfrow = c(2,3))
hist(norm)
hist(binom)
hist(pois)
hist(exp)
